# ============================================================================
# CSP DECISION LOG — 2026-04-13
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# STATUS: Temporary production bridge
#
# REASON: gtag.js injects runtime inline scripts that cannot be pre-hashed.
# Cloudflare Pages injects per-request challenge scripts with changing hashes.
# Both make pure hash-based script-src impossible on static hosting.
# 'unsafe-inline' in script-src is the documented Google recommendation
# for sites using gtag.js without server-side nonce capability.
# Ref: https://developers.google.com/tag-platform/security/guides/csp
#
# ADDITIONAL CONTEXT: GA property G-XR2CJ9LZ2Z is linked to Google Ads
# conversion tag AW-11518581694. That tag loads Facebook Pixel, Pinterest
# Tag, and Bing UET at runtime via GTM. All domains below were derived
# from actual CSP violation logs dated 2026-04-13.
#
# TARGET: Replace with nonce-based CSP via Cloudflare Worker.
# Backlog: "Replace temporary CSP unsafe-inline bridge with Worker
#          nonce-based CSP (strict-dynamic + per-request nonce)"
#
# SCOPE OF TEMPORARY RELAXATION:
#   - 'unsafe-inline' added ONLY to script-src
#   - Every domain listed was validated against actual error logs
#   - No wildcards except where Google uses subdomain-based routing
#
# VALIDATION CHECKLIST (run after every deploy):
#   [ ] No CSP errors in browser DevTools console
#   [ ] Network tab: filter "collect" — requests completing (200)
#   [ ] GA4 > Realtime: showing pageview activity
#   [ ] Cloudflare Web Analytics dashboard: receiving data
# ============================================================================

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; img-src 'self' data: https://www.google-analytics.com https://www.googletagmanager.com https://www.google.com https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net https://www.facebook.com https://analytics.google.com; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://www.googletagmanager.com https://static.cloudflareinsights.com https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net https://connect.facebook.net https://s.pinimg.com https://bat.bing.com https://capi-automation.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com https://www.google.com; connect-src 'self' https://www.google-analytics.com https://region1.google-analytics.com https://*.google-analytics.com https://analytics.google.com https://www.google.com https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net https://connect.facebook.net https://www.facebook.com https://bat.bing.com https://ct.pinterest.com https://capi-automation.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com https://cloudflareinsights.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self';

/index.html
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate

/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/sitemap.xml
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400, s-maxage=86400
  Content-Type: application/xml

/robots.txt
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400, s-maxage=86400
